svg.title: MiiMOSA
svg.desc: Founded in 2015, present in France and Belgium, MiiMOSA is the European leader in crowdfunding on agricultural and food topics. To revolutionize the financing of this theme, 4 financing offers have been developed and 2 platforms: MiiMOSA (local agriculture and food) and MiiMOSA transition (agricultural, food and energy transition).
